<h2 class="sectionedit1"><a name="short" id="short">short</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
The short keyword is a data type modifier that is used to declare short integer
variables. See the <a href="../data_types" class="wikilink1" title="data_types">data types</a> page.
</p>

